Class UnloadedTrigger

java.lang.Object
io.github.syst3ms.skriptparser.lang.UnloadedTrigger
public class UnloadedTrigger extends Object
A trigger-to-be whose contents haven't been loaded yet. It will be loaded based on its event's loading priority.
